We are creating this network to share the best of Black experiences with the diaspora. ALL content is created by Black Content Creators (filmakers, documentarians, Real Estate, Biblical and Black Diasporic Historians, Finance, Health/Wellness, Lifestyle, Music, Poetic Arts, Family, Clean Eating, etc.) sharing their best with us all.

We are asking that you support this independent Blac media outlet by purchasing a subscription, liking/sharing our IG page, help us get to 500 subscribers within our firts quarter, RECOMMEND Content Creators and suggestions for future programming.

Join us for our Virtual Pre-Launch event, July 28th at 7PM for more information DM or email us at support@sablenetwork.tv

IG: @sablenetworktv

@famjenks @tscllc  @sablenetworktv

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021 tagging @chocolvtepapii. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'ΚΑΝΑΙ ANDERSON @ChocolvtePapii Interested in starting an E-Com Brand/ Online Business but don't know where to start? Let me break it down in 10 easy steps (A thread)'.

Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'ΚΑΝΑΙ ANDERSON @ChocolvtePapii 1.Look for product validation of winning products in your intended (niche/product) use websites like Amazon, Walmart, etc. and use the "best selling" or "hot now" categories 2.Find a supplier via Alibaba.com & secure 1 main supplier for your product and two backups Find quality Manufacturers, Suppliers, Exporters, Importers,... alibaba.com'.

Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'ΚΑΝΑΙ ANDERSON @ChocolvtePapii 3.Create your brand identity: colors (Two Max), Logo, & Brand Story (people buy emotion & justify with logic) 4.Create Social Media & Content (use Canva & drop some type of tips/value about niche, industry, or product) All content should either Inform, Inspire, or entertain'.

Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'ΚΑΝΑΙ ANDERSON @ChocolvtePapii 5.Build website using Shopify, make sure lead magnet is setup properly, & other plugins to boost conversions 6.Reach out to all family, friends & mutuals to generate initial revenue and sell first set of inventory or Pre- Orders (if it's en-route)'.

Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ΚΑΝΑΙ ANDERSON @ChocolvtePapii 7.Start influencer marketing to grow your page & appeal to semi-warm audience (spend no more than $25-50 per page initially) 8.Convert repeat customers to affiliates (they already like the brand & product) incentivize them more to continue telling everyone why they should too'.

Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'ΚΑΝΑΙ ANDERSON @ChocolvtePapii 9.Launch PPC Marketing FB Ads & get creatives (ads) made using a website like fiverr.com 10.Record tasks you do repetitively.. outsource those to a VA, via Fiverr or Upwork and begin freeing your time so you can focus on the high- income activities of the businesss fiverr. Get Everything You Need Starting at $5 Fiverr fiverr.com'.

Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'E-Commerce comes with an abundance of problems & fires you have to consistently put out No reason you should do this alone For the same cost of a cup of coffee, you can invest into yourself with the purchase of my E-Book the "The ECom Bible" & get 75% off today link in my bio Jul 2020-Jul 1, 2021 compared to Jul 1, 2019-Jun 30, 2020 Total sales $140,831.04 Online Store $136,723.65'.
Photo by Buy Black Economics on August 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"Sometimes you have to stop being scared and just go for it. Either it will work out, or it won't. That's life."'.
